<Sync time="12869.691"/>
na Institutu 
<Event desc="unintelligible" type="noise" extent="instantaneous"/>
 rusiske akademije 
<Event desc="unintelligible" type="noise" extent="instantaneous"/>
, torej inštitutu za slavistiko ruske akademije znanosti. 
